4x4 or even 6x6 would probably work, using a reasonably-sized square table.<br /><br />(a + b)^2 = a^2 + b^2 + 2*a*b<br />((a + b)^2 - a^2 - b^2)/2 = a*b<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Thu Oct 23, 2008 5:40 pm</p><hr />
